      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:63:20",
      "text": [
        " إِنَّ أَمِيرَ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ ( عليه السلام ) رَأَى قَاصّاً فِي الْمَسْجِدِ فَضَرَبَهُ بِالدِّرَّةِ وَ طَرَدَهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said that: ‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> saw a story-teller in the Masjid, so he<sup>asws</sup> hit him with the whip and expelled him’."
        ]
      }
